Date: 1994-04-06

Title: A Parity Invariant Regularization in 3-D Quantum Electrodynamics

Authors: Tadahiko Kimura

Comments: 7 pages, CHIBA-EP-76, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 92 (1994) 693-698

We regularize the 3-D quantum electrodynamics by a parity invariantPauli-Villars regularization method. We find that in the perturbation theorythe Chern-Simons term is not induced in the massless fermion case and inducedin the massive fermion case.